al-Abadi spoke in Davos,
Switzerland, today, where he's
attending

03:46.126 --> 03:48.562 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the World Economic Forum.

03:48.562 --> 03:52.899 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HAIDER AL-ABADI, Iraqi Prime
Minister: I have to rely on the
information I have. A, we don't

03:52.899 --> 03:56.603 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
know if they have been
kidnapped. They're missing.
We're still looking for them.
There

03:56.603 --> 04:02.642 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
