anybody get from that?

04:06.346 --> 04:10.250 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Other Iraqi
officials and some Western
security sources have said two

04:10.250 --> 04:14.654 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Shiite militias are the top
suspects in the abductions.

04:14.654 --> 04:18.692 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
