unspecified -- quote -- "hostile
acts" and allegedly plotting to

04:32.439 --> 04:35.041 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
destroy the country's unity.

04:35.041 --> 04:39.579 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
