died overnight when Islamist
gunmen attacked a popular
beachside

04:44.718 --> 04:49.022 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
restaurant. It happened in
Mogadishu, and the Islamist
group Al-Shabaab claimed
responsibility.

04:49.022 --> 04:54.528 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
