a young job seeker was
electrocuted

05:11.344 --> 05:15.982 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
when he climbed a transmission
tower in protest. Unemployment
in the North African nation has

05:15.982 --> 05:21.454 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
