revolution that launched the
Arab Spring.

05:21.454 --> 05:26.526 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And back in this country, Wall
Street rallied as oil pushed
back above $32 dollars a barrel.

05:26.526 --> 05:32.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
