21:43.536 --> 21:45.704 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the page.

21:45.704 --> 21:50.176 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: It will be back.
You never escape it. And I think
