33:06.685 --> 33:10.789 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID NAZAR: CVUSD's director of
technical services, Israel
Oliveros, provides the technical

33:10.789 --> 33:13.458 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
