33:13.458 --> 33:14.292 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ISRAEL OLIVEROS, Director of
Technical Services, Coachella
Valley Unified School District:

33:14.292 --> 33:18.964 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We run power through a conduit
