34:27.265 --> 34:29.234 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Smith says that has to change.

34:29.234 --> 34:33.371 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MEGAN SMITH: There is a lot of
creativity that American people
have.

34:33.371 --> 34:36.574 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so whether it's going to
