Wheels program is playing

35:28.059 --> 35:31.463 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a vital role in her education.

35:31.463 --> 35:36.334 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ANISA PEREZ: I want to do this
