Charities.

42:45.863 --> 42:50.435 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DR. JULIE LEVY: I'm very
confident we're going to see
this nationally as a successful
model

42:50.435 --> 42:52.970 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
