42:52.970 --> 42:57.275 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ADITHYA SAMBAMURTHY: In many
ways, Operation Catnip is the
best-case scenario for trap,

42:57.275 --> 43:01.045 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
neuter, return. It's
well-funded, with a steady
