43:15.293 --> 43:19.964 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ADITHYA SAMBAMURTHY: Dr. Patrick
Foley teaches at California
State University in Sacramento.

43:19.964 --> 43:24.202 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
