43:54.732 --> 43:58.636 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ADITHYA SAMBAMURTHY: According
to Foley's calculations,
Operation Catnip would need

43:58.636 --> 44:04.242 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
