44:47.785 --> 44:52.390 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In a statement sent to us, a
spokesperson said: "The
organization is reassessing its

44:52.390 --> 44:55.860 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
programs, including its support
of trap, neuter, return, but
they will honor all existing
grant

44:55.860 --> 44:58.563 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
commitments."

44:58.563 --> 45:03.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Although one of the biggest
funders of trap, neuter and
return is having second
thoughts,

45:03.100 --> 45:09.607 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the feral cat movement continues
